      <title>新日铁在美国收购案中举步维艰，寻找下一步行动</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/nippon-steel-left-hunting-for-plan-b-as-us-takeover-flounders</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新日本制铁公司斥资 141 亿美元收购美国钢铁公司的交易周四濒临失败，美国总统乔·拜登准备阻止这笔交易，此举将使这家日本巨头寻找其他增长选择，而东京官员则将研究此举对两个盟友的外交影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-05/nippon-steel-left-hunting-for-plan-b-as-us-takeover-flounders</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 05 Sep 2024 07:51:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
